This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with object detection and pose estimation. The use of deep learning also suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The focus on scalability and robotics applications suggests that it could also belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. Finally, the use of benchmarks and evaluation metrics suggests that it could belong to the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
